usk-x-to-add-defendants-to-garm-advertisers-lawsuit-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EX%20is%20suing%20several%20major%20brands%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20Mars%2C%20Lego%2C%20Nestl%C3%A9%2C%20and%20Shell%2C%20alleging%20their%20participation%20in%20an%20ad%20industry%20initiative%20called%20the%20Global%20Alliance%20of%20Responsible%20Media%2C%20GARM%2C%20was%20tantamount%20to%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20%26quot%3Bcollectively%20withhold%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20advertising%26quot%3B%20from%20X%20after%20Musk's%20takeover%20of%20the%20company%2C%20then%20known%20as%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EX%20had%20claimed%20the%20alleged%20boycott%20resulted%20in%20it%20becoming%20%26quot%3Ba%20less%20effective%20competitor%20to%20other%20social%20media%20platforms%20in%20the%20sale%20of%20digital%20advertising%20and%20in%20competing%20for%20user%20engagement%20on%20its%20platform.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20joint%20motion%20filed%20on%20Wednesday%20seeking%20to%20dismiss%20the%20case%2C%20the%20defendants%20said%20the%20lawsuit%20was%20instead%20%26quot%3Ban%20attempt%20to%20use%20the%20courthouse%20to%20win%20back%20the%20business%20X%20lost%20in%20the%20free%20market%20when%20it%20disrupted%20its%20own%20business%20and%20alienated%20many%20of%20its%20customers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202019%2C%20GARM%20was%20an%20initiative%20of%20the%20advertiser%20trade%20body%20The%20World%20Federation%20of%20Advertisers%20that%20aimed%20to%20provide%20the%20industry%20with%20a%20common%20language%20and%20frameworks%20to%20help%20categorize%20the%20kind%20of%20content%20that%20advertisers%20tend%20to%20want%20to%20avoid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20categories%20ranged%20from%20obviously%20harmful%20content%20like%20child%20sex-abuse%20imagery%2C%20to%20content%20like%20violence%2C%20which%20different%20sorts%20of%20advertisers%20have%20varying%20risk%20appetites%20toward.%20The%20uptake%20of%20these%20frameworks%20was%20voluntary.%20X%20was%20previously%20itself%