%5C%224473%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWalmart%20reported%20its%20first-quarter%20results%20on%20Thursday.%3Cp%3EJay%20L%20Clendenin%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-stores-history-old-photos%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWalmart%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20first-quarter%20revenues%20of%20%24168%20billion%2C%20up%204%25%20from%20last%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUS%20sales%20were%20boosted%20by%20shoppers%20rushing%20to%20get%20ahead%20of%20tariff-related%20price%20hikes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWalmart's%20CFO%20said%20customers%20should%20expect%20price%20rises%20soon.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWalmart's%20strong%20first%20quarter%20underscores%20that%20the%20retailer%20views%20tough%20times%20as%20an%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20reported%20first-quarter%20revenues%20of%20%24168%20billion%2C%20up%204%25%20from%20last%20year%20on%20a%20constant%20currency%20basis%2C%20and%20a%203%25%20rise%20in%20profit%20to%20%247.3%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20delivered%20a%20solid%20first%20quarter%20in%20a%20dynamic%20operating%20environment.%20We're%20serving%20customers%20and%20members%20in%20more%20ways%2C%20which%20is%20fueling%20our%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20CEO%20Doug%20McMillon%20said%20in%20the%20earnings%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20sales%20were%20lifted%20by%20shoppers%20rushing%20to%20get%20ahead%20of%20potential%20price%20hikes%20related%20to%20new%20tariffs%20on%20China%20and%20other%20countries%20announced%20during%20the%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYear-over-year%20foot%20traffic%20to%20Walmart%20stores%20was%20up%20an%20estimated%204.5%25%20in%20April%2C%20after%20being%20down%20in%20February%20and%20March%2C%20likely%20due%20to%20shopper%20concerns%20about%20prices%20and%20supply%20constraints%2C%20according%20to%20Placer.ai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stock%20rose%202.6%25%20in%20premarket%20trading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20CNBC%20after%20the%20earnings%20were%20released%2C%20Walmart's%20CFO%20John%20David%20Rainey%20said%20shoppers%20should%20expect%20increased%20prices%20in%20the%20near%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20wired%20for%20everyday%20low%20prices%2C%20but%20the%20magnitude%20of%20these%20increases%20is%20more%20than%20any%20retailer%20can%20absorb%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20more%20than%20any%20supplier%20can%20absorb.%20And%20so%20I'm%20concerned%20that%20the%20consumer%20is%20going%20to%20start%20seeing%20higher%20prices.%20You'll%20begin%20to%20see%20that%2C%20likely%20towards%20the%20tail%20end%20of%20this%20month%2C%20and%20then%20certainly%20much%20more%20in%20June.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalmart%20also%20reported%20major%20growth%20in%20revenue%20from%20its%20membership%20programs%2C%20with%20global%20membership%20fee%20income%20up%20nearly%2015%25.%20The%20company%20doesn't%20disclose%20publicly%20how%20many%20Plus%20members%20it%20has%2C%20but%20it%20is%20estimated%20at%20more%20than%2015%20million%2C%20according%20to%20Barclays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEO%20Doug%20McMillon%20gave%20a%20preview%20of%20the%20results%20in%20early%20April%20at%20Walmart's%20investor%20meeting%2C%20shortly%20after%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20ratcheted%20up%20tariffs%20on%20imports%20from%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcMillon%20said%20that%20two-thirds%20of%20what%20Walmart%20sells%20in%20the%20US%20is%20sourced%20domestically%2C%20and%20said%20the%20retailer's%20broad%20product%20assortment%20and%20experienced%20merchandising%20teams%20were%20well-suited%20to%20handle%20the%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20just%20manage%20it%20in%20a%20way%20that%20mix%20becomes%20a%20strength%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20CFO%20John%20David%20Rainey%20said%20at%20the%20time%20that%20fluid%20situations%20like%20this%20one%20have%20historically%20seen%20Walmart%20win%20customers%20over