mal%20paper%20usually%20contains%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrinking-from-plastic-bottles-can-increase-diabetes-risk-new-research-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebisphenols%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20class%20of%20chemicals%20used%20to%20manufacture%20plastics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22bitcoin%20receipt%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5594fdb3dd0895994d8b4595%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222281%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EReceipts%20are%20usually%20printed%20on%20thermal%20paper%20using%20heat.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FPeter%20Nicholls%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20famous%20bisphenol%2C%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fwhat-is-bpa%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBPA%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20been%20linked%20to%20heart%20disease%2C%20decreased%20fertility%2C%20breast%20and%20prostate%20cancers%20and%2C%20in%20children%2C%20asthma%20and%20neurodevelopmental%20issues.%20BPA%20has%20been%20phased%20out%20of%20US%20products%20over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20including%20receipts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS0269749123012344%3Fvia%253Dihub%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudies%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20found%20that%20many%20receipt%20manufacturers%20have%20replaced%20the%20BPA%20with%20its%20cousin%20BPS%2C%20which%20is%20banned%20in%20Europe%20for%20use%20in%20food%20containers%2C%20considered%20a%20reproductive%20toxin%20by%20the%20state%20of%20California%2C%20and%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20breast%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20touch%20a%20receipt%20that's%20coated%20in%20BPS%2C%20the%20toxic%20chemical%20can%20quickly%20enter%20your%20body%20by%20absorbing%20through%20your%20skin%2C%20according%20to%20recent%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20nonprofit%20watchdog%20Center%20for%20Environmental%20Health%20tested%20receipts%20from%2032%20major%20retailers%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fceh.org%2Flatest%2Fpress-releases%2Ftouching-1-receipt-for-10-seconds-results-in-exposure-to-the-chemical-bps-above-the-safe-limit%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efound%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20touching%20one%20for%2010%20seconds%20would%20expose%20someone%20to%20enough%20BPS%20to%20legally%20require%20a%20warning%20in%20California.%20Under%20the%20state's%20Proposition%2065%2C%20businesses%20must%20provide%20warnings%20about%20significant%20exposures%20to%20chemicals%20that%20cause%20cancer%20or%20reproductive%20harm.%20The%20CEH%20delivered%20a%20legal%20notice%20to%20those%2032%20retailers%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChemicals%20used%20in%20plastic%20materials%20need%20to%20be%20properly%20vetted%20for%20safety%2C%26quot%3B%20Trasande%20said.%20%26quot%3BInsofar%20as%20chemicals%20are%20identified%20to%20be%20toxic%20to%20human%20health%2C%20we%20have%20safer%20alternatives%20that%20should%20be%20considered.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20called%20electronic%20receipts%20%26quot%3Ban%20important%20positive%20step%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d1d66420-976b-4e97-9494-95425b9d07ae%5C%22%3EMicroplastics%20in%20receipts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnderlying%20the%20bisphenols%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20plastic.%20Though%20Trasande%20said%20there%20is%20much%20more%20definitive%20research%20on%20the%20health%20effects%20of%20many%20chemicals%20in%20plastics%2C%20emerging%20science%20about%20the%20proliferation%20of%20plastics%20themselves%20throughout%20the%20human%20body%20is%20not%20comforting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plastic%20items%20that%20surround%20us%20all%20in%20our%20homes%2C%20workplaces%2C%20schools%2C%20and%20even%20the%20outdoors%20are%20shedding%20tiny%20particles%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteens-win-fifty-thousand-for-ultrasound-microplastic-filtration-device-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emicroplastics%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20or%2C%20when%20they%20get%20really%20tiny%2C%20nanoplastics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20minuscule%20plastics%20build%20up%20in%20our%20bodies.%20They've%20been%20found%20in%20almost%20every%20human%20body%20tissue%20researchers%20have%20checked%2C%20from%20the%20brain%20to%20the%20lining%20of%20the%20arteries.%20Their%20health%20impacts%20are%20not%20yet%20clear%2C%20but%20they've%20been%20linked%20to%20chronic%20inflammation%2C%20lung%20and%20colon%20cancers%2C%20reproductive%20health%20issues%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicroplastics-artery-plaque-mysterious-link-stroke-heart-attack-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eheart%20attack%20and%20stroke%3C%2Fa%3E%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20limits%20to%20what%20I%20can%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20Trasande%20said.%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20there%20are%20so%20many%20steps%20we%20can%20take%20to%20reduce%20our%20exposure%20to%20chemicals%20of%20concern%20and%20particularly%20micro-%20and%20nanoplastics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeclining%20paper%20receipts%20is%20one%20of%20them.%20On%20the%20whole%2C%20though%2C%20Trasande%20said%20the%20world%20needs%20to%20reduce%20its%20plastic%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20business%20as%20usual%20continues%2C%20plastics%20production%20is%20expected%20to%20triple%20by%202060%2C%20according%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20Environment%20Programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrasande%20said%20a%20global%20plastics%20treaty%20would%20help.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fsustainability%2Fclimate-energy%2Fun-sets-date-extra-session-finalize-plastics-treaty-2025-03-03%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20is%20set%20to%20resume%20negotiations%20for%20such%20a%20treaty%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20origina