ed-on-first-long-distance-hike-mistakes-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elong-distance%20walks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20were%20intrigued.%20We%20wondered%20if%20we%20could%20do%20it%20at%20our%20ages%20%E2%80%94%2082%20and%2073%20%E2%80%94%20and%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20a%20try%20this%20April.%20While%20a%20lot%20of%20it%20was%20difficult%2C%20we're%20so%20glad%20we%20went.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22799f98c0-509c-4967-a430-821d7d49f680%5C%22%3EBefore%20starting%20our%20journey%2C%20we%20adapted%20to%20the%20elevation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20staying%20in%20Quito%20for%20two%20days%20to%20adapt%20to%20the%20elevation%2C%20we%20hired%20an%20Uber%20for%20%2445%20to%20drive%20us%20two%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20to%20our%20hostel%20in%20Sigchos.%20We%20were%20the%20only%20guests%20there.%20Because%20it%20was%20the%20rainy%20season%2C%20most%20of%20the%20people%20we%20saw%20weren't%20other%20trekkers%2C%20but%20innkeepers%2C%20shepherds%2C%20and%20farmers%2C%20looking%20tough%20and%20hardy%20from%20daily%20physical%20work%20at%20high%20elevation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20night%2C%20after%20a%20filling%20home-cooked%20dinner%20of%20potato%20soup%2C%20beans%2C%20corn%2C%20cheese%2C%20and%20homemade%20bread%2C%20I%20slept%20restlessly%2C%20worrying%20about%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarathon-runner-exercises-aging-longevity-paddleboarding-yoga-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efitness%20levels%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20if%20we'd%20get%20soaked%2C%20as%20afternoon%20thunderstorms%20were%20common.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20morning%2C%20we%20established%20our%20pattern%20of%20leaving%20before%207%20a.m.%20after%20a%20hearty%20breakfast.%20Though%20each%20day%20only%20involved%206-8%20miles%20of%20trail%2C%20we%20had%20to%20pace%20ourselves%20because%20high-elevation%20hiking%20takes%20much%20more%20exertion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20terrain%20was%20steep%2C%20uneven%2C%20and%20muddy%2C%20plus%20