%3D%5C%22b221d731-2f05-4870-971e-2f604802218c%5C%22%3EThe%20hostels%20were%20fantastic%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20hostel%20in%20Isinlivi%20felt%20like%20a%20boutique%20hotel%2C%20with%20home-cooked%20meals%2C%20wifi%2C%20a%20fireplace%2C%20bar%2C%20spa%2C%20sauna%2C%20and%20even%20yoga%20classes%2C%20perfect%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ftreatments%2Fhow-to-get-rid-of-a-stiff-neck%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erelaxing%20tight%20muscles%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Since%20the%20only%20other%20hikers%20there%20were%20a%20friendly%20Israeli%20couple%20and%20their%20adult%20son%2C%20the%20owner%20offered%20us%20a%20cottage%20overlooking%20the%20valley%20for%20the%20price%20of%20a%20single%20room.%20It%20was%20so%20luxurious%2C%20Barry%20wanted%20to%20stay%20another%20night%2C%20but%20I%20felt%20we%20had%20barely%20gotten%20into%20the%20rhythm%20of%20hiking%2C%20so%20we%20left%20the%20next%20day.%20Now%20I%20wish%20we'd%20stayed!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20later%20hostels%20were%20not%20as%20elegant%2C%20but%20they%20too%20offered%20%26quot%3BTurkish%20saunas%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaunas-hot-new-hangout-spot-social-cold-plunge-class-review-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esteam%20baths%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20fragrant%20eucalyptus%20leaves.%20The%20second%20night%2C%20I%20lingered%20in%20the%20hostel's%20steam%20room%20for%20a%20full%20hour%2C%20breathing%20in%20the%20eucalyptus%20and%20listening%20to%20the%20thrum%20of%20heavy%20rain%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22953%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20with%20a%20llama%20while%20hiking%20on%20a%20trail.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68225abe3fe8d39283659ee9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22803%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20and%20her%20husband%20hiked%206-8%20miles%20a%20day%20and%20often%20saw%20wildlife%20and%20plants%20along%20the%20way.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Louisa%20Rogers%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22607ad40f-753e-43c7-a873-03b655465da0%5C%22%3EThe%20last%20day%20was%20the%20toughest%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20day%20we%20climbed%20a%20tiring%203%2C650%20feet%20to%20the%20rim%20of%20the%20lake.%20As%20I%20looked%20down%20into%20the%20caldera%2C%20I%20admired%20the%20turquoise%20water%2C%20but%20knew%20we%20still%20had%20more%20than%20an%20hour's%20walk%20to%20our%20final%20destination%2C%20the%20touristy%20village%20of%20Quilotoa.%20As%20it%20turned%20out%2C%20because%20we%20missed%20our%20turnoff%2C%20it%20took%20us%20an%20extra%20hour%2C%20and%20en%20route%20we%20got%20drenched%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20hostel%20caretakers%20in%20Quitoloa%20took%20good%20care%20of%20us.%20The%20husband%20built%20a%20wood%20fire%20where%20we%20huddled%20while%20we%20dried%20our%20wet%20clothes%20and%20consumed%20his%20wife's%20lentil%20soup%20and%20homemade%20bread.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2295fe0d11-7105-4f8b-a008-1635ed460bb3%5C%22%3EIt%20was%20difficult%2C%20but%20beautiful%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStrenuous%20as%20the%20trek%20was%2C%20I%20found%20the%20combination%20of%20simple%20beauty%2C%20invigorating%20mountain%20air%2C%20and%20the%20unthinking%20act%20of%20putting%20one%20foot%20in%20front%20of%20the%20other%20almost%20mystical.%20I%20was%20enchanted%20by%20the%20beauty%20%E2%80%94%20deep%20valleys%20lined%20with%20ridges%20of%20different%20shades%20of%20green%20and%20lush%20pastures%20dotted%20with%20llamas%20and%20cows.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20seeing%20green%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20I'm%20back%20into%20my%20sea-level%20routines%2C%20I'm%20still%20inspired%20by%20those%20strong%2C%20wiry%20shepherds%20and%20farmers.%20Thanks%20to%20them%2C%20I've%20set%20a%20higher%20bar%20for%20myself.%20Walking%20the%20Quilotoa%20Loop%20reminded%20me%20of%20what%20I'm%20still%20capabl