20C%2B%2B.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESutter%20also%20talks%20about%20how%20job%20applicants%20can%20stand%20out.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20think%20that%20coding%20languages%20are%20static%2C%20just%20a%20string%20of%20letters%20and%20numbers%20for%20humans%20to%20communicate%20with%20machines%20and%20software.%20But%20Herb%20Sutter%2C%20a%20tech%20leader%20at%20Citadel%20Securities%2C%20says%20otherwise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20major%20languages%20that%20are%20in%20heavy%20use%20are%20living%20languages%2C%26quot%3B%20Sutter%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20we%20see%20C%2B%2B%2C%20Rust%2C%20C%2C%20and%20Python%20continuing%20to%20evolve.%20Our%20landscape%20is%20always%20changing%2C%20and%20it's%20important%20to%20stay%20abreast%20of%20those%20developments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20market%20maker%2C%20Citadel%20Securities%20needs%20to%20be%20ready%20to%20match%20buyers%20and%20sellers%20and%20provide%20liquidity%20to%20institutional%20and%20retail%20investors%20worldwide.%20The%20company%20is%20focused%20on%20mastering%20C%2B%2B%2C%20because%20speed%20and%20execution%20are%20everything.%20It's%20considered%20a%20more%20specialized%20coding%20language%20that%20is%20often%20used%20at%20high-frequency%20trading%20firms%20and%20exchanges.%20Better%20use%20and%20understanding%20of%20C%2B%2B%20can%20translate%20to%20faster%20systems%20and%20fewer%20coding%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESutter%20joined%20in%202024%20from%20Microsoft%20to%20spearhead%20its%20training%20initiatives%20on%20C%2B%2B%2C%20which%20is%20used%20extensively%20throughout%20Citadel%20Securities'%20technology.%20As%20one%20of%20the%20more%20senior%20technologists%20at%20the%20firm%2C%20it's%20Sutter's%20day%20job%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20evolution%20of%20coding%20languages%20to%20make%20sure%20Ken%20Griffin's%20market%20maker%20is%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20latest%20and%20greatest.%20But%20even%20less%20experienced%20coders%20have%20something%20to%20gain%20by%20familiarizing%20themselves%20with%20the%20fresh%20features%20that%20come%20with%20new%20versions%20of%20C%2B%2B%3B%20one%20edge%20is%20standing%20out%20in%20the%20interview%20process%20to%20nab%20a%20job%20at%20Citadel%20Securities%2C%20which%20can%20fetch%20up%20to%20%24350%2C000%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.citadelsecurities.com%2Fcareers%2Fdetails%2Fcredit-software-engineer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejobs%20requiring%20C%2B%2B%20experience%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20this%20Q%26amp%3BA%2C%20Sutter%20discusses%20how%20the%20firm%20is%20embracing%20a%20new%20version%20of%20C%2B%2B%20that%20isn't%20even%20set%20to%20be%20fully%20released%20until%20next%20year%2C%20and%20two%20pieces%20of%20advice%20that%20can%20help%20engineers%20stand%20out%20from%20the%20crowd.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow've%20you%20been%20and%20what's%20keeping%20you%20busy%20these%20days%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20at%20Citadel%20Securities%20for%20about%20six%20months.%20Can%20you%20believe%20it%3F%20And%20it%20has%20been%20great.%20I've%20been%20drinking%20from%20a%20firehose%20because%20there's%20lots%20of%20exciting%20work%20to%20do%20and%20new%20things%20I'm%20being%20exposed%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20particularly%20enjoyed%20seeing%20how%20the%20firm%20is%20adopting%20the%20important%20and%20immediately%20useful%20elements%20of%20the%20new%20standards%2C%20even%20without%20waiting%20for%20the%20ink%20to%20officially%20dry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20things%20I'm%20especially%20excited%20about%20is%20C%2B%2B's%20async%20framework%20that's%20coming%20in%20the%20next%20standard%20that%20will%20ship%20about%20a%20year%20from%20now.%20Async%20use%20of%20C%2B%2B%20is%20a%20big%20deal%20because%20we%20are%20all%20increasingly%20needing%20to%20do%20things%20concurrently%20and%20in%20parallel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%5BEditor's%20note%3A%20%26quot%3Basync%26quot%3B%20is%20shorthand%20for%20asynchronous%20%E2%80%94%20code%20that%20can%20run%20in%20the%20background%20without%20freezing%20your%20app.%20It's%20a%20new%20framework%20that%20helps%20developers%20write%20faster%2C%20smoother%20programs%20by%20handling%20tasks%20like%20downloading%20files%20or%20crunching%20numbers%20without%20making%20users%20wait.%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20realize%20until%20I%20joined%20Citadel%20Securities%20just%20how%20much%20that%20framework%20is%20already%20used%20at%20the%20firm%2C%20including%20for%20our%20US%20equities%20trading.%20Working%20at%20Citadel%20Securities%20is%20almost%20like%20living%20in%20the%20future%20in%20that%20we're%20already%20diving%20deep%20into%20technologies%20that%20will%20eventually%20be%20widely%20used.%20That's%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20wearing%20glasses%20is%20holding%20a%20microphone%20and%20speaking%20to%20people%20inside%20an%20office%20space.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6824e42668a292900801544f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECitadel%20Securities'%20Herb%20Sutter%3Cp%3ECitadel%20Securities%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20exactly%20is%20an%20async%20framework%2C%20and%20why%20is%20it%20becoming%20increasingly%20important%20to%20have%20things%20work%20concurrently%20and%20in%20parallel%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConcurrency%20is%20the%20idea%20of%20doing%20more%20than%20one%20thing%20at%20a%20time%2C%20which%20we're%20always%20trying%20to%20do%20in%20a%20network-cloud%20world%2C%20whether%20that's%20waiting%20for%20cloud%20capacity%20or%20AI%20tokens.%20Parallelism%20is%20when%20you%20have%20one%20huge%20computation%20to%20do%2C%20but%20would%20like%20to%20spread%20elements%20out%20over%20multiple%20machines%20to%20get%20the%20answer%20more%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20impresses%20me%20most%20about%20C%2B%2B26's%20async%20framework%20is%20that%20it%20can%20handle%20both%20of%20those%20elements%20%E2%80%94%20the%20one%20that%20involves%20hiding%20and%20waiting%2C%20and%20the%20other%20that's%20doing%20many%20different%20things.%20Those%20are%20such%20different%20things.%20Doing%20them%20both%20well%20in%20one%20framework%20is%20pretty%20amazing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20think%20of%20what%20a%20trading%20system%20has%20to%20do.%20Requests%20for%20trades%20are%20flying%20across%20the%20wire%20all%20the%20time.%20You%20never%20know%20when%20the%20client%20is%20going%20to%20want%20to%20buy%20or%20sell%2C%20so%20as%20a%20market%20maker%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20ready%20at%20all%20times.%20And%20that%20means%20being%20very%20responsive%2C%20very%20efficient%2C%20and%20super%20fast.%20Execution%20is%20extremely%20important%2C%20and%20that's%20why%20we're%20investing%20in%20the%20async%20framework.%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20some%20of%20the%20advantages%20that%20you're%20seeing%20being%20an%20early%20adopter%20or%20a%20first%20mover%20in%20this%20new%20C%2B%2B%20standard%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Citadel%20Securities%2C%20using%20the%20things%20today%20that%20everyone%20else%20is%20going%20to%20be%20using%20months%20or%20years%20from%20now%20builds%20muscle%20and%20familiarity%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20for%20something%20as%20core%20as%20an%20async%20framework.%20Beyond%20that%2C%20we%20have%20been%20providing%20feedback%20and%20suggesting%20tweaks%20to%20the%20standard%20that%20are%20being%20adopted.%20Because%20we're%20using%20the%20new%20standard%20in%20production%20and%20at%20scale%2C%20we're%20able%20to%20play%20a%20role%20in%20evolving%20the%20language%2C%20which%20has%20been%20great.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20would%20a%20prospective%20hire%20show%20off%20their%20C%2B%2B%20skills%3F%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20way%20you%20can%20show%20off%20your%20C%2B%2B%20skills%20is%20simply%20by%20talking%20about%20what%20you're%20looking%20forward%20to%20most%20in%20C%2B%2B26%2C%20describing%20the%20features%20that%20have%20helped%20you%2C%20or%20sharing%20something%20you've%20learned%20recently.%20I%20want%20to%20know%20that%20you're%20that%20curious%20and%20that%20you're%20focused%20on%20continuous%20learning%2C%20and%20that's%20true%20more%20generally%2C%20regardless%20of%20language.%20It's%20important%20to%20be%20able%20to%20demonstrate%20curiosity%20and%20knowledge%20about%20software%20advancements%20%E2%80%94%20and%20to%20show%20that%20you%20understand%20that%20there's%20more%20than%20one%20tool%20out%20there%20and%20that%20you%20know%20how%20to%20use%20them%20together.%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20your%20advice%20to%20young%20engineers%20interested%20in%20joining%20Citadel%20Securities%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20encourage%20young%20engineers%20to%20get%20as%20much%20work%20experience%20as%20possible%20as%20early%20as%20possible.%20I%20went%20to%20the%20University%20of%20Waterloo%20in%20Canada%2C%20which%20has%20a%20well-known%20co-op%20program%20that%20served%20me%20incredibly%20well%2C%20but%20there%20are%20many%20others%20out%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20is%20to%20get%20some%20work%20experience%20so%20that%20by%20the%20time%20you%20graduate%2C%20you%20have%20spent%20a%20significant%20amount%20of%20time%20using%20your%20skills%20in%20a%20real-world%20environment.%20The%20biggest%20differentiator%20we%20see%20among%20candidates%20is%20their%20ability%20to%20use%20technology%20to%20solve%20commercial%20problems.%20Ultimately%2C%20knowing%20data%20structures%2C%20languages%2C%20and%20the%20like%20are%20important%20tools%20in%20the%20toolkit%2C%20but%20what%20will%20really%20set%20you%20apart%20is%20your%20ability%20to%20solve%20business%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcitadel-