d%20better%20at%20assembly%2C%20he%20increased%20his%20rates%20%E2%80%94%20but%20only%20up%20to%20a%20certain%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20notice%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20charge%20a%20lot%20for%20certain%20jobs%2C%20and%20I%20try%20to%20never%20be%20too%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mendez.%20He%20adjusts%20his%20usual%20hourly%20rate%20of%20%2465-%2470%20an%20hour%20seasonally%2C%20charging%20more%20in%20the%20summer%20when%20demand%20spikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a48f49b-c1cf-4f33-b740-4e88792f5004%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20typical%20day%20in%20the%20life%3A%20E-biking%20between%20jobs%20and%20earning%20%24100%20a%20day%20minimum%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMendez%20starts%20most%20of%20his%20workdays%20at%209%20a.m.%20During%20the%20week%2C%20he%20finishes%20between%203%20and%204%20p.m.%3B%20on%20Saturdays%2C%20he%20wraps%20early%20at%202%20p.m.%3B%20and%20he%20takes%20Sunday%20off%2C%20using%20that%20day%20to%20reset%20and%20do%20volunteer%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20typical%20day%20features%20two%20to%20three%20jobs%20that%20last%20between%20one%20and%20two%20hours.%20In%20the%20summer%2C%20which%20is%20busy%20season%2C%20he'll%20complete%20up%20to%20four%20jobs%20a%20day%3A%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20moving%20and%20need%20a%20lot%20of%20furniture%20built%20or%20rebuilt.%20I%20can't%20tell%20you%20how%20many%20times%20people%20tell%20me%20I've%20saved%20their%20marriage%20or%20saved%20their%20relationship%20because%20I'm%20taking%20the%20time%20to%20put%20something%20together%20for%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20could%20accept%20more%20gigs%20if%20he%20wanted%20to%2C%20but%20he%20prefers%20a%20lighter%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22michael%20taskrabbit%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68224deb3fe8d39283659c6e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMendez%20sold%20his%20car%20and%20bought%20an%20e-bike.%20He%20says%20his%20active%20commute%20saves%20him%20money%20and%20stress.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Michael%20Mendez%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20meet%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20work%20all%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20were%20looking%20to%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20cash%20flow%20in%2C%20I%20could%20just%20set%20my%20hours%20until%209%20p.m.%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20my%20preference.%20I%20don't%20like%20to%20stress%20my%20body%20out%20for%20too%20long.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20he%20doesn't%20feel%20the%20need%20to%20earn%20more%20than%20he%20already%20does%2C%20which%20ranges%20from%20%242%2C000%20during%20slower%20months%20and%20%244%2C000%20during%20busy%20months%2C%20according%20to%20earnings%20screenshots%20viewed%20by%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20main%20thing%20is%2C%20as%20long%20as%20I%20make%20at%20least%20%24100%20a%20day%2C%20I'm%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20very%20simple.%20I%20definitely%20practice%20minimalism.%20I'm%20not%20very%20into%20owning%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20or%20spending%20my%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20chunk%20of%20his%20day%20is%20spent%20commuting%20between%20gigs.%20Up%20until%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20ago%2C%20he%20drove%20and%20dealt%20with%20daily%20stressors%20such%20as%20sitting%20in%20traffic%20and%20looking%20for%20parking.%20Now%2C%20he%20commutes%20on%20his%20e-bike%2C%20which%20saves%20him%20time%2C%20money%2C%20and%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20bikes%2C%20I%20love%20doing%20bikepacking%20trips%2C%20and%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'How%20can%20I%20fit%20this%20in%20with%20my%20work%20life%3F'%26quot%3B%20said%20Mendez.%20%26quot%3BMy%20bike%20shop%20has%20e-bikes%2C%20and%20I%20found%20the%20best%20one%20for%20city%20riding%20and%20for%20holding%20my%20tools.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20sold%20his%20car%2C%20has%20been%20relying%20on%20his%20e-bike%20and%20the%20BART%20train%20to%20get%20around%20ever%20since%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20it's%20been%20a%20dream%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226de14bbd-55ac-434c-95f3-b7a00c572663%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20succeed%20on%20Taskrabbit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20every%20personality%20type%20is%20right%20for%20Taskrabbit.%20It's%20a%20social%20job%20that%20involves%20soft%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20have%20it%20in%20you%20to%20put%20yourself%20out%20there%20because%20you're%20kind%20of%20selling%20yourself%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mendez.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20be%20very%20presentable%20and%20be%20good%20with%20the%20clients.%20You%20learn%20a%20lot%20about%20people%2C%20and%20how%20to%20give%20them%20their%20space.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreate%20a%20detailed%20bio%20that%20explains%20your%20skillset%20and%20exactly%20what%20tasks%20you%20offer%20to%20give%20yourself%20the%20best%20chance%20of%20attracting%20customers.%20Don't%20limit%20your%20clientele%20by%20setting%20parameters%20such%20as%20a%20two-hour%20minimum%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BSome%20people%20do%20the%20two-hour%20minimum%2C%20but%20that's%20one%20thing%20that%20could%20shy%20a%20client%20away%20from%20picking%20me%2C%20and%20I%20want%20no%20reason%20for%20a%20client%20to%20not%20pick%20me.%20I%20just%20want%20my%20profile%20to%20be%20as%20welcoming%20as%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221680%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22michael%20taskrabbit%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68224e11c6ad288d1480b24c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22796%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMendez's%20Taskrabbit%20profile%20features%20a%20detailed%20'About%20me'%20section%20and%20more%20than%201%2C500%20reviews.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Michael%20Mendez%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEqually%20important%20to%20building%20out%20a%20welcoming%20profile%20is%20knowing%20your%20limit%2C%2