0ensure%20I%20got%20some%20good%20sleep%2C%20I%20gradually%20began%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20baby%20and%20only%20do%20that%2C%20while%20my%20husband%20took%20care%20of%20my%20recovery.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20honesty%20is%20striking%20%E2%80%94%20something%20every%20new%20mom%20can%20likely%20relate%20to.%20The%20late-night%20Google%20searches%2C%20the%20endless%20advice%2C%20the%20contradictory%20dos%20and%20don%E2%80%99ts%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20it%20adds%20to%20the%20noise.%20And%20Priyanka%E2%80%99s%20been%20there%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EWhen%20in%20doubt%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20first%20thing%20new%20mothers%20do%2C%20including%20me%2C%20is%20to%20browse.%20That%20itself%20gives%20a%20lot%20of%20stress.%20The%20research%20we%20do%20gives%20us%20a%20lot%20of%20information%2C%3Cem%3E%20which%20is%2C%20mostly%20contradicting%20what%20the%20doctor%20says.%20When%20we%20stop%20doing%20this%2C%20I%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20our%20mental%20load%20is%20off%20our%20heads%2C%20and%20new%20mothers%20can%20think%20clearly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Priyanka%2C%20the%20early%20days%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F111340%2Fmothering-is-in-the-love-not-in-the-blood%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emotherhood%3C%2Fa%3E%20felt%20less%20like%20an%20emotional%20whirlwind%20and%20more%20like%20checking%20things%20off%20a%20to-do%20list.%20It%20became%20a%20job%20%E2%80%94%20one%20she%20threw%20herself%20into%2C%20completely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EWhile%20taking%20care%20of%20my%20baby%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20bring%20in%20emotions%2C%20and%20I%20had%20a%20to-do%20list%20in%20my%20mind%20and%20struck%20off%20things%20as%20I%20finished%20them.%20I%20never%20thought%20about%20myself.%20It%20was%20always%20the%20baby.%20I%20think%20mothers%20just%20power%20through%20everything%2C%20small%20or%20big%20challenges%2C%20after%20they%20give%20birth%20to%20their%20baby.%20The%20secret%20is%20to%20just%20go%20with%20the%20flow%20and%20not%20think%20much%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20with%20raw%20honesty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20daily%20life%20a%20little%20more%20manageable%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20bring%20in%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESo%20as%20to%20ease%20the%20daily%20duties%20as%20a%20mother%2C%20we%20hired%20a%20help%2C%20to%20bathe%20and%20massage%20the%20baby%2C%20wash%20her%20clothes%20and%20more.%20For%20other%20tasks%20of%20playing%20with%20her%20or%20reading%20her%20a%20book%20we%20have%20my%20parents%20and%20in-laws%20around%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20routines%2C%20Priyanka%20has%20let%20go%20of%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20strict%20schedule%20%E2%80%94%20something%20she%20once%20held%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EI%20just%20know%20what%20I%20have%20to%20finish%20during%20the%20day.%20There%20is%20no%20timing%20set%20for%20any%20of%20the%20tasks.%20I%20was%20someone%20who%20had%20a%20schedule%20for%20everything%20but%20now%20I%20have%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20not%20having%20a%20schedule%20and%20that%20it%20is%20all%20about%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20demands.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20just%20three%20months%2C%20this%20new%20mother%20has%20learned%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20lessons%20of%20all%20%E2%80%94%20that%20motherhood%20rarely%20goes%20by%20the%20book.%20And%20sometimes%2C%20the%20best%20way%20to%20show%20up%20is%20simply%20to%20flow%20with%20the%20chaos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEarly%20to%20rise%2C%20last%20to%20sleep%3A%20how%20mothers%20made%20it%20work%2040%20years%20ago%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20smartphones%20to%20set%20reminders.%3Cbr%3ENo%20appliances%20to%20make%20cooking%20easier.%3Cbr%3ENo%20washing%20machines%20to%20lighten%20the%20load.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20what%20daily%20life%20looked%20like%20for%20Sai%20Chitra%20Venkatesh%20and%20Bhavani%20Krishnamurthy%20when%20they%20became%20new%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F99660%2Fincredible-mother-nurtures-33-children-tulsi-parihar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emothers%20in%20the%201980s%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarried%20into%20the%20same%20home%2C%20Bhavani%20(65)%20and%20Chitra%20(55)%20say%20living%20in%20a%20joint%20family%20made%20everything%20manageable%20%E2%80%94%20even%20joyful.%20It%20gave%20them%20the%20support%2C%20reassurance%2C%20and%20shared%20strength%20that%20every%20new%20mother%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20co-sisters%20settled%20in%20for%20a%20nostalgic%20chat%20with%20us%2C%20taking%20a%20warm%2C%20honest%20walk%20down%20memory%20lane%20%E2%80%94%20back%20to%20the%20days%20when%20motherhood%20looked%20very%20different%2C%20yet%20felt%20just%20as%20consuming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20daughter%20was%20born%20in%201985%2C%20and%20I%20was%2026.%20While%20my%20husband%20had%20just%20launched%20his%20business%2C%20I%20relied%20heavily%20on%20my%20mother-in-law%2C%20brother-in-law%2C%20and%20Chitra%20with%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20work.%20And%20today%20I%20can%20tell%20it%20was%20the%20three%20of%20them%20who%20raised%20my%20daughter%20while%20I%20took%20care%20of%20the%20home%2C%20made%20meals%20for%20all%2C%20and%20did%20all%20the%20household%20chores%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Bhavani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-54-1747035200.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mother%20day%20mental%20load%20on%20moms%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-54-1747035200.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-54-1747035200-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-54-1747035200-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-54-1747035200-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-54-1747035200-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-427035%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFrom%20brewing%20coffee%20to%20feeding%20the%20dog%2C%20Bhavani%20and%20Chitra%20stayed%20on%20their%20feet%2C%20while%20others%20looked%20after%20the%20little%20ones.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20never%20just%20one%20person%20doing%20it%20all%E2%80%94someone%20was%20always%20around%20to%20lend%20a%20hand.%20While%20Bhavani%20focused%20on%20her%20baby%20and%20managed%20the%20kitchen%2C%20Chitra%20took%20care%20of%20everything%20else%E2%80%94often%20without%20stopping%20to%20take%20a%20breath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20brewing%20coffee%20for%20the%20whole%20family%20to%20making%20sure%20meals%20were%20on%20time%2C%20to%20even%20feeding%20the%20dog%2C%20Chitra%20was%20constantly%20on%20the%20move.%20And%20while%20she%20did%20that%2C%20Bhavani%2C%20their%20brother-in-law%2C%20and%20their%20mother-in-law%20cared%20for%20the%20little%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBeing%20in%20a%20joint%20family%20can%20be%20a%20big%20blessing%2C%20provided%20one%20overlooks%20all%20the%20differences%20in%20opinion.%20Any%20task%20or%20challenge%20was%20made%20simpler%20and%20dealt%20with%20easily%20because%20there%20were%20so%20many%20to%20help%20around%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20came%20to%20any%20issues%20with%20the%20baby%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chitra%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20the%2080s%2C%20the%20roles%20in%20most%20households%20were%20sharply%20divided%20%E2%80%94%20men%20earned%20the%20money%2C%20and%20women%20took%20care%20of%20everything%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20they%20brought%20in%20the%20money%2C%20we%20provided%20all%20the%20care%20the%20kids%20and%20others%20needed.%20So%20our%20goals%20and%20aims%20were%20very%20clear%20and%20as%20a%20team%20we%20worked%20towards%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ladies%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20admit%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20words%20like%20%3Cem%3Epostpartum%20depression%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%3Cem%3Ebaby%20blues%3C%2Fem%3E.%20They%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20terms%20for%20the%20hormonal%20upheavals%20or%20mental%20load%2C%20but%20that%20didn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20the%20emotions%20weren%E2%80%99t%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHence%2C%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20pay%20attention%20to%20any%20of%20those.%20We%20only%20lived%20every%20day%20for%20the%20love%20we%20had%20for%20our%20children%2C%20and%20that%20gave%20us%20so%20much%20clarity%20on%20the%20tasks%20we%20had%20to%20carry%20out%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Chitra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20day%20was%20full%20to%20the%20brim%20%E2%80%94%20waking%20up%20before%20everyone%20else%2C%20sleeping%20after%20the%20whole%20household%20had%20turned%20in.%20There%20were%20no%20shortcuts%2C%20just%20relentless%20energy%20and%20deep%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20how%20a%20day%20looked%20for%20us%2030%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20today%2C%20when%20we%20look%20back%2C%20we%20only%20wonder%20how%20we%20found%20the%20mental%20strength%20and%20physical%20energy%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do%20so%20much%2C%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20Bhavani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20for%20Chitra%20was%20the%20emotional%20dependence%20her%20daughter%20had%20on%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20Maa%2C%20I%20need%20soap%20for%20a%20shower%2C%20to%20Maa%2C%20where%20is%20my%20blanket%20in%20bed%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%20was%20her%20only%20go-to%20person.%20Anything%20missing%20in%20the%20house%20had%20to%20be%2